{"tid":1853024,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"[超現實]《惊了!袁国勇不会公开的秘密!》","createTime":"2020-01-30T17:39:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T03:39:19.000Z","uid":109631,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"59b72f98760801bff75fa522e0269b3178355497","tid":1853024,"uid":109631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T17:39:17.000Z","msg":"香港大学李嘉诚医学院微生物学系传染病学讲座教授袁国勇, 也是我们知道的沙士英雄<br />\n可他还有一个不能放在台面上的名字--<br />\n<strong>变态科学家</strong><br />\n没有其他爱好, 只爱推理实验<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/597009/org/f3ac93ec1cd37020cfaf44df4a28e4bd.jpg/OHT561XFRF5Vg1-Z1zpPOhmQEkyE5_ijInk79SJ5O_U\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F597009%2Forg%2Ff3ac93ec1cd37020cfaf44df4a28e4bd.jpg%2FOHT561XFRF5Vg1-Z1zpPOhmQEkyE5_ijInk79SJ5O_U&h=5a9dcfa0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n袁国勇每天都与他唯一的朋友&quot;福尔摩斯&quot;谈天<br />\n<br />\n他的玛嘉烈医院10A病房和10B实验室, 如果进去了就不能离开了!<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/01/200121_CR_%E8%A2%81%E5%9C%8B%E5%8B%87.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F01%2F200121_CR_%25E8%25A2%2581%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%258B%2587.jpg&h=4b87b3a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你看他老头多高兴, 嘴角的微笑, 心里发毛了!<br />\n为了测试药物 Ribavirin和高剂量类固醇的效果, 10A病人都半死不活! <br />\n骨枯, 偏瘫, 脑死亡 什么都有!<br />\n<br />\n袁国勇不單是一个变态, 还是一个港毒, 想国人自生自灭!<br />\n早在2003年, 他已经說要&quot;封关&quot;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cyDWjPq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcyDWjPq.jpg&h=2eee68af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gFyLc9q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgFyLc9q.jpg&h=1ccfb7fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2020年, 还是說要&quot;封关&quot;, 要港毒!<br />\n<img src=\"https://medicalinspire.com/web/wp-content/uploads/sb-instagram-feed-images/2231958069716410128_7936285639low.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedicalinspire.com%2Fweb%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsb-instagram-feed-images%2F2231958069716410128_7936285639low.jpg&h=adaa8c45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n一个爱实验的港毒, 啥意思呀? <br />\n10个确诊, 8个不是香港人, 现在这8个人在玛嘉烈医院10A的水深火热中!<br />\n被袁国勇的变态实验强奸! 他们有没有痊愈, 如何痊愈, 不是很重要<br />\n<img src=\"https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/cookeys.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/YUEN_newlogo_ULHealth_1000_teamplate.jpg?auto=format&amp;w=830\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Fcookeys.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2FYUEN_newlogo_ULHealth_1000_teamplate.jpg%3Fauto%3Dformat%26w%3D830&h=59844588&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n5天造疫苗, 袁国勇說正在&quot;测试阶段&quot;<br />\n<br />\n造了疫苗, 就說不&quot;封关&quot;了<br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcS2QTZlXpDeEl3KdjxnOk-fSjh7iTtHVtXncDPql8xfaLeMk7qM&amp;s\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcS2QTZlXpDeEl3KdjxnOk-fSjh7iTtHVtXncDPql8xfaLeMk7qM%26s&h=cf8b6fc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n因为他需要测试的病人呀!<br />\n<br />\n让香港人当小白鼠就好, 咱們国人要保住我们的生命, 不为变态和港毒服务, 不要千万去香港!<br />\n<img src=\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/proxy/mVt-E0DKpp-5os8DeA9F8HhvWksFwLIzCxNcifdRgzWJYLO-LXG1TmstZSV75OFlvIj_oIieLfy5vnoap4arOw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh6.googleusercontent.com%2Fproxy%2FmVt-E0DKpp-5os8DeA9F8HhvWksFwLIzCxNcifdRgzWJYLO-LXG1TmstZSV75OFlvIj_oIieLfy5vnoap4arOw&h=52298648&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eb7e4bb537bd6dfcc6963398f91a140058c95e69","tid":1853024,"uid":109631,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T17:39:54.000Z","msg":"厲害了我的国勇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a3fc46245b7f8be46fe792aa035869b84c5b168","tid":1853024,"uid":202876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T21:39:08.000Z","msg":"認同請分享好人一生平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9243a71f0cd7ed77608b698e8206dd93d461deb6","tid":1853024,"uid":67171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T22:00:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3a2b8eb8ca1d332c3d749bec2f64188da78ea6df","tid":1853024,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T22:06:04.000Z","msg":"放上微博啦，係到推做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f48cb16c1650fd843afcbc5caeb4ba933fa134c","tid":1853024,"uid":109631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a2b8eb8ca1d332c3d749bec2f64188da78ea6df","tid":1853024,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T22:06:04.000Z","msg":"放上微博啦，係到推做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T03:39:19.000Z","msg":"我冇呢啲嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都諗緊點先比大陸人睇到"}]}